
# Document Edition v_1.0
# Important Tips, Tricks and Work-arounds on Windows Server

# Resetting Windows Server Trail for 180 days up to 06 Times - Applicable on Windows 2016,2019,2022
# Run cmd as Administator
# To check the License current State 
SLMGR -DLV
# To reset the Windows License up to 6 times
SLMGR -REARM
# Reboot the Server Node, Windows Trail will reset to 180 days
# Source - https://www.uubyte.com/blog/what-happens-when-windows-server-evaluation-expires/

